00:21:00,298 --> 00:21:01,118
What?

353
00:21:01,222 --> 00:21:02,202
Wait, is that credible? Is that true?

354
00:21:02,306 --> 00:21:03,016
I don't know.

355
00:21:03,119 --> 00:21:06,889
I mean, he's been very confused and a little
hard to figure out, but I did get a name.

356
00:21:07,005 --> 00:21:08,725
Peter. Peter harrison.

