00:21:11,412 --> 00:21:12,832
What's happening here
is what happened to me.

360
00:21:12,938 --> 00:21:15,008
She had a patient, dheied, he's
blaming her.

361
00:21:15,117 --> 00:21:17,547
Well, I need to check online
and see if I can find anything.

362
00:21:17,657 --> 00:21:21,292
In the meantime, can you please just check
on jennifer and how peter harrison died?

363
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:23,345
Yeah.

364
00:21:23,450 --> 00:21:25,310
Yeah, I'll check on her when I go in.

365
00:21:25,418 --> 00:21:27,738
We'll talk about the rest of this later.

366
00:21:27,848 --> 00:21:30,103
Whatever you want.

367
00:21:41,236 --> 00:21:42,641
Callin' it a night?

